ll/125\r\n* config/default: Link some rules to their styleguide justifications by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/124\r\n* config/rails: Broader ERB exclude paths by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/126\r\n* Allow RailsViewRenderShorthand errors to be autocorrected by @mgriffin in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/114\r\n* Fix Styleguide link in default.yml by @sampart in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/129\r\n* Add link to Style Guide from README by @sampart in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/130\r\n* config/default: Remove some redundant `Enabled: true` for cops by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/128\r\n* Add Rails recommendations to styleguide by @sampart in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/131\r\n* Add contribution instructions, code of conduct, and codeowners by @bensheldon in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/122\r\n* Replace custom `RailsApplicationRecord` and `RailsRenderInline` cops with their upstream equivalent by @bensheldon in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/123\r\n* STYLEGUIDE: For each styleguide recommendation, link to the RuboCop rule by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/132\r\n* STYLEGUIDE: `UnusedBlockArgument` is in `Lint` not `Style` by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/134\r\n* config/default: Upstream cop disables since this is the central place by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/127\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @ydah made their first contribution in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/111\r\n* @mgriffin made their first contribution in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/114\r\n* @sampart made their first contribution in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/129\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/compare/v0.19.0...v0.20.0", "mentions_count": 5}
