ithub.com/bensheldon", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bensheldon/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": true}, "content_type": "application/octet-stream", "state": "uploaded", "size": 24576, "download_count": 1, "created_at": "2022-10-13T15:38:24Z", "updated_at": "2022-10-13T15:38:25Z", "browser_download_url": "https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/releases/download/v0.19.0/rubocop-github-0.19.0.gem"}], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/github/rubocop-github/tarball/v0.19.0", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/github/rubocop-github/zipball/v0.19.0", "body": "## Significant Changes\r\n\r\n* config/default: Unset `DisabledByDefault: true` by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/119\r\n* Accessibility Cops have been migrated to https://github.com/github/rubocop-rails-accessibility\r\n\r\n\r\n## Other Changes\r\n* Fix .rubocop.yml example by @orhantoy in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/104\r\n* Migrate accessibility rubocop rule `ImageHasAlt` from dotcom to erblint-github by @bolonio in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/105\r\n* Migrate accessibility rubocop rule `NoRedundantImageAlt` from dotcom to erblint-github by @bolonio in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/106\r\n* Migrate accessibility rubocop rule `NoPositiveTabindex` from dotcom to erblint-github by @bolonio in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/107\r\n* Migrate accessibility rubocop rule `LinkHref` from dotcom to erblint-github by @bolonio in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/108\r\n* Add improvements to styleguide by @elenatanasoiu in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/113\r\n* Delete GitHub/Accessibility cops; point to `rubocop-rails-accessibility` by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/118\r\n* fix(STYLEGUIDE.md): remove extra opening code block by @francisfuzz in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/115\r\n* README, guides: Clean up leftover `GitHub/Accessibility` cop references by @issyl0 in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/120\r\n* Separate Ruby (`rubocop-github`) from Rails (`rubocop-github-rails`) cops and rules to disambiguate rule inheritance from custom cops by @bensheldon in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/121\r\n* fix(STYLEGUIDE.md): use list item instead of codeblock by @francisfuzz in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/116\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @bolonio made their first contribution in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/105\r\n* @elenatanasoiu made their first contribution in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/113\r\n* @francisfuzz made their first contribution in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/115\r\n* @bensheldon made their first contribution in https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/pull/121\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/github/rubocop-github/compare/v0.18.0...v0.19.0", "mentions_count": 6}
